{"tid":2297362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"強國遼寧家居水龍頭開水用火機一點就著  火遁定炎之呼吸？","createTime":"2020-11-23T08:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T03:59:38.000Z","uid":121021,"like":277,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":138,"replies":[{"pid":"82ae31f64995817df5b5da66597acddefefd6078","tid":2297362,"uid":121021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"中國遼寧省盤錦市四營村驚爆一起公眾安全事故，有村民表示家用水龍頭流出的自來水「可以點燃」，洗手的時候常常感覺洗不乾淨，同村100多戶家裡都出現相同狀況，而且「這個情況已經很久了」；更離譜的是，早在夏天時他們就曾向自來水公司反映，對方卻說管不了，放任這種危害公安的潛在風險多個月！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/23/2896980-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F23%2F2896980-PH.jpg&h=6cfff231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲文女示範家裡自來水點火就燒的情況。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，文姓女子在微博上發文表示，打開家裡水龍頭流出自來水後，竟可用打火機點燃，「這個情況已經很久了」，每次使用清潔劑洗手、洗碗後，手上還是有殘留清潔劑、洗不乾淨的感覺，「我們家那個村子裡吧，我們這100多家是這樣。就夏天的時候去找過一次自來水公司，他們說管不了」，文女只好透過微博求助。<br />\n<br />\n仔細觀察文女的曝光影片，當她打開水龍頭、拿打火機靠近，現場瞬間冒出熊熊大火，而且隨著自來水流出完全沒有熄滅的跡象，讓人看了不免心驚膽跳；消息曝光後，相關單位馬上關閉該地區的自來水供應，改用臨時調水的方法供應民生用水，同時也成立專案小處展開調查，進行水質檢測、原因分析的動作，表示未來有結果將第一時間進行公告。<br />\n<br />\n對此，許多中國網友紛紛大酸政府，消息曝光引發民眾注意才重視，紛紛表示：「不反映到微博，有相關單位關注嗎？」「好幾年了，不上熱搜估計這輩子就這樣了」、「我想問一問，為什麼只有媒體曝光了才會有人管」、「果然上了熱搜就管用」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dsT0Kbg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdsT0Kbg.gif&h=b86ca800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三立新聞：<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=852874&amp;utm_source=setn.com&amp;utm_medium=viewall&amp;utm_campaign=viewallnews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D852874%26utm_source%3Dsetn.com%26utm_medium%3Dviewall%26utm_campaign%3Dviewallnews&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnfrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=544b102c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D852874%26utm_source%3Dsetn.com%26utm_medium%3Dviewall%26utm_campaign%3Dviewallnews&h=0d10f138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=852874&amp;utm_source=setn.com&amp;utm_medium=viewall&amp;utm_campaign=viewallnews</a>"},{"pid":"7ccef480807dc1f4b0e987b40fa82075dec42450","tid":2297362,"uid":59931,"like":237,"dislike":1,"score":236,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"係生命之水！"},{"pid":"3cc48dfa9a24e2eb947ede4d5ce658fbfab5e9c7","tid":2297362,"uid":14918,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"噴火槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc37721fa6ae40b7a28c1a56737e1b83f963b12a","tid":2297362,"uid":37427,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"vodka!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8216a8de6b126f14e68bbea4dc200ed320d127cf","tid":2297362,"uid":286178,"like":328,"dislike":0,"score":328,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6EQP1G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6EQP1G.jpg&h=625fad6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fb5a2e278333187bb1565c9a5437c964eaed230","tid":2297362,"uid":31237,"like":170,"dislike":0,"score":170,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:36:19.000Z","msg":"煤氣貴過水 仲唔感謝黨？"},{"pid":"7580cc186391629f8fec616495454da5a41378c0","tid":2297362,"uid":70487,"like":300,"dislike":2,"score":298,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"此水必火"},{"pid":"a700d3a5bd26c1dd22c7860138c15a58a6c4d64e","tid":2297362,"uid":199893,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:37:35.000Z","msg":"都幾撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid